	(text_box "The reason tha we don't have the symbols for the battery tabs in this sheet as this is sheet is used 15 times, so we layout it once and then duplicate that layout. This wouldn't work if we duplicated the battery tabs with it also as the relation of these protection components to the battery tabs is slightly different for some of the cells.\n\n"
